metadata.name: Crypto trading dark elf - First class #1/30
metadata.description:
< crypto trading dark elf: 7 >

While the crypto market was going through a bear market, I toured various countries with the dark elf 「Cott」 

Because Cott contracted 「a disease that breaks her back when she sits in economy and business seats」 she always sat in first class and traveled to other countries And at the end of a long trip, "Oh, I'm tired of walking around now" She decided to return to her homeland, uttering words like those of a drunkard muttering at dawn after wandering around the local hotspots 

"Oh, before that..." Cott decided to stop by Jeju Island, a large island in Korea, before returning home 

"There's a garage for my collection there. I'm going to include one of the two LaFerraris I bought this time in my collection"

Just like an otaku buying another Blu-ray for collection or propagation, Cott plans to buy two identical supercars, put one in a garage in Jeju Island, and bring one back to Seoul to ride

Cott triumphantly ordered champagne and whiskey from the flight attendant

Dark elf with a lot of money are extravagant today as always
